---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Specified Commercial Transactions Act — Asukaru">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Notation Based on the Specified Commercial Transactions Act</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">特定商取引法に基づく表示</p>

    <table class="mt-12 w-full text-sm">
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top w-1/3">Business Name</th>
          <td class="py-4">合同会社飛鳥瑠 (Godo Kaisha Asukaru)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">CEO</th>
          <td class="py-4">Askar Karasawa (唐沢 飛鳥瑠)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Address</th>
          <td class="py-4">〒273-0118 千葉県鎌ケ谷市西道辺１－３－４０１</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Phone</th>
          <td class="py-4">070-1072-0222</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Email</th>
          <td class="py-4">contact@asukaru.com</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">URL</th>
          <td class="py-4">https://asukaru.com</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Pricing</th>
          <td class="py-4">As stated on each service page or in individual quotations/contracts. All prices are displayed inclusive of tax.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Additional Costs</th>
          <td class="py-4">Internet connection fees and other communication costs are borne by the customer. For bank transfers, transfer fees are borne by the customer.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Payment Methods</th>
          <td class="py-4">Credit card (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, JCB), bank transfer.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Payment Timing</th>
          <td class="py-4">Credit card: charged immediately at time of purchase. Subscriptions: charged on the contract start date and each subsequent renewal date. Bank transfer: within 14 days of invoice issuance.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Service Delivery</th>
          <td class="py-4">SaaS services: account access is provided promptly upon payment confirmation. Custom development: as specified in the individual contract.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Contract Duration</th>
          <td class="py-4">Subscriptions: monthly plans auto-renew every month; annual plans auto-renew every year. Contracts continue automatically until cancelled by the customer. Custom development: as specified in the individual contract.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Cancellation</th>
          <td class="py-4">Subscriptions: customers may cancel at any time from their account management page. Cancellation takes effect from the next renewal date; service remains available until the end of the current billing period. No pro-rata refunds. Custom development: subject to cancellation terms in the individual contract.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">Refunds</th>
          <td class="py-4">Due to the nature of digital services, refunds are generally not available after service delivery has commenced. If there is a material defect in the service, please contact us to discuss resolution.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="py-4 pr-6 text-left text-gray-500 font-medium align-top">System Requirements</th>
          <td class="py-4">Latest versions of Google Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Microsoft Edge. Internet connection required.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</Layout>
